Similarly, `‖f * g‖ₙ_[∞]` is the L∞ norm of `f * g`, which is `sup {‖f a * g a‖₊ | a ∈ α}`.

So we need to show `‖f * g‖ₙ_[∞] ≤ ‖f‖ₙ_[0] * ‖g‖ₙ_[0]`.

